DISCLAIMER FOR RESEARCH USE

This software is intended for academic and defensive security research purposes
only. The anonymous public repository includes benign payload files for smoke
testing. Real malware samples, if separately obtained through a controlled
research channel, must be handled strictly for evaluating the steganography
defense mechanisms described in the accompanying research paper.

Users must:
- NOT use this software for malicious purposes
- NOT execute any malware samples outside of isolated research environments
- Comply with all applicable laws and regulations
- Use this software responsibly and ethically
